name: Recycled T Shirt Tote Bag Hillary Clinton
description:
Hillary Clinton supporters will just love this bag! Made from a recycled T shirt depicting the Comeback Kid herself, this tote is perfect for anything you need to carry with you!

Each original ReTeez Tote is handmade from previously loved, discarded T shirts that would otherwise end up in local landfills or shipped across the world to wreck havoc on local economies 

All of our recycled bags are reinforced with interfacing, lined with rescued fabric and comes complete with an inner pocket. Sturdy and fashionable, ReTeez totes are perfect for books, shopping or the gym. 

Approximate Measurements: 14” x 16”
Lining Color: Navy – one interior slot pocket
Handles Color: Navy

Handles: 20” – Perfect to fling over your shoulder
